snippet.title: 20th Century Video Almanac (3DO) - Gameplay Footage
snippet.description:
Here is a video for 20th Century Video Almanac for the 3DO. This was strictly an educational title and contained pictures, audio and videos from important times in the 20th century...

This video contains footage that includes 3 short video clips from different points in history...
